{"id":2878,"date":"2012-04-12T11:08:59","date_gmt":"2012-04-12T15:08:59","guid":{"rendered":"http:\/\/www.dailyhadithonline.com\/?p=2878"},"modified":"2024-01-30T13:11:06","modified_gmt":"2024-01-30T09:11:06","slug":"believers-nar-forever","status":"publish","type":"post","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2012\/04\/12\/believers-nar-forever\/","title":{"rendered":"Hadith on Iman: Sinful believers will not stay in Hellfire forever"},"content":{"rendered":"<p>Abu Sa\u2019id al-Khudri reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201c<strong>Allah will admit the people of Paradise into Paradise among whomever He wills, due to His mercy, and He will admit the people of Hellfire into Hellfire, then Allah will say: Look for those with faith in their hearts as much as a seed and bring them out! Then, they will be brought out from it as burnt charcoal. They will be cast into the river of life and sprout just as a seed sprouts on the side of the riverbank. Have you not seen that it comes out yellow and entwined<\/strong>?\u201d<\/p>\n<p>Source: S\u0323ah\u0323i\u0304h\u0323 al-Bukha\u0304ri\u0304 22,\u00a0S\u0323ah\u0323i\u0304h\u0323 Muslim 184<\/p>\n<p>Grade: <em><strong>Muttafaqun Alayhi\u00a0<\/strong><\/em>(authenticity agreed upon) according to Al-Bukhari and Muslim<\/p>\n<p align=\"right\">\u0639\u064e\u0646\u0652 \u0623\u064e\u0628\u0650\u064a \u0633\u064e\u0639\u0650\u064a\u062f\u064d \u0627\u0644\u0652\u062e\u064f\u062f\u0652\u0631\u0650\u064a\u0650\u0651 \u0623\u064e\u0646\u064e\u0651 \u0631\u064e\u0633\u064f\u0648\u0644\u064e \u0627\u0644\u0644\u064e\u0651\u0647\u0650 \u0635\u064e\u0644\u064e\u0651\u0649 \u0627\u0644\u0644\u064e\u0651\u0647\u064f \u0639\u064e\u0644\u064e\u064a\u0652\u0647\u0650 \u0648\u064e\u0633\u064e\u0644\u064e\u0651\u0645\u064e \u0642\u064e\u0627\u0644\u064e \u064a\u064f\u062f\u0652\u062e\u0650\u0644\u064f \u0627\u0644\u0644\u064e\u0651\u0647\u064f \u0623\u064e\u0647\u0652\u0644\u064e \u0